                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000115-75-defend653 t18000115-75-punish448"></join>
               Death
            </rs>. (Aged 24.)</p>
               <p>The prisoner was recommended by the prosecutor to his Majesty's mercy, on account of the respectability of his family.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury, before The LORD CHIEF BARON.</p>
